task.summary: Implemented piece; concrete constructor and abstract canYouMoveTo method.
Piece now has enum for black/white/empty. Pieces now in seperate package. Changed references to pieces in the main package.
Moved graphics for basic chess into the basic chess package.
Added onclick event handler for moving pieces.
Added method for getting a linked list of all non-empty pieces on the board.
Basic main method to create a basic chess board.
Added an image field into pieces.
Redid the graphics package so that it works, also still provides abstract classes for each variant.
Redid the basic chess graphics implementation to make use of the new abstract classes in the graphics package.
Made several minor changes to the graphics.
Replaced tif files with png versions. Further improved graphics implementation. Started to implement graphical piece movement.
Fixed various issues with the graphics.
Fixed bishop move checking. Fixed queen move checking.
